*bind-9.2.5-r2 (15 Apr 2005)

  15 Apr 2005; Konstantin Arkhipov <voxus@gentoo.org> -bind-9.2.5-r1.ebuild,
  +bind-9.2.5-r2.ebuild, -bind-9.3.1.ebuild, +bind-9.3.1-r1.ebuild,
  +files/named.rc6-smart_pid_fix:
